▶️ Full Run Workflow
1. Build images
packer build packer/windows-server.pkr.hcl
packer build packer/windows-client.pkr.hcl
2. Create VMs
cd terraform
terraform init
terraform apply
3. Configure everything
cd ../ansible
ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini site.yml
